{
  "stem": "20088.8",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they made a bit buffet with food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then-- and fireworks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a wonderful party.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they said, well, now, you have to go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, of course, we're all dying to go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they said, well, it will still take a little while because, you know, we have to wait for ships to come to take you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they registered everybody then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think that the Red Cross English people, English-speaking people came in and registered where we want to go, where we had come from.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were going to organize it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was one Australian who got very friendly with my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, look, why do you want to go back to Holland?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have [INAUDIBLE] this terrible war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what you want to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am a sheep farmer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've got lots of land and lots of sheep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'll marry you, and you can come with me to Australia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And your daughter can come too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, you know, I'll be very good for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother said, no, but I've got my husband and my son now to go, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he tried to convince her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, she wouldn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later, he still go to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got a letter once from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Said he married and he was quite happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was-- [LAUGHS] that was a very early offer of marriage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And, I mean, you know, my mother still looked pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I say, it was just stress and a shaved-- [INAUDIBLE] hair had started to grow a bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we were still quite skeletal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after a little while, a big troop transport, a New Zealand troop transport ship, the came.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
